org.omg.space.xtce

Class BinaryDataEncodingType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.omg.space.xtce.DataEncodingType
      • org.omg.space.xtce.BinaryDataEncodingType

  • public class BinaryDataEncodingType
extends DataEncodingType
    For binary data or for integer, float, string, or time data that is not in any of the known encoding formats. For any data that is not encoded in any of the known integer, float, string, or time data formats use a To/From transform algorithm.

    Java class for BinaryDataEncodingType complex type.
